title: Be Comfortable With Who You Are

description:
Are you comfortable enough to play the role God has given you? John 3:27 says, “A man must be content to receive the gift which is given him.” If you’ll use what you do have, God will breathe on it.----Visit https://joelosteen.com to receive daily updates and encouragement from Joel Osteen.----Have you followed Joel Osteen on Instagram? https://instagram.com/joelosteen.
